  "intro_paragraph": "Inspired by Chraime—from the Arabic for 'hot'—these vegan patties capture the essence of the spicy Friday night fish course. Tofu and wakame seaweed provide a savory, oceanic texture, formed into ktzi'tzot (patties). They are baked, then simmered in a classic Djerban sauce of rich tomatoes, peppers, and garlic."
